Package vhdlgenerator.generator

Class FileGenerator

java.lang.Object
vhdlgenerator.generator.FileGenerator
public class FileGenerator extends Object
this class generate the code for the VHDL file. this class take information from the class Port and write those information to the file.
Author:
DOUDOU DIAWARA If a null object is passed in argument to any method, then a NullPointerException will be thrown.
